\begin_layout Subsubsection
Entropy-conservative numerical state function
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
A key ingredient in the development of an entropy-stable DG scheme is a
 two-point numerical state function that satisfies the following condition
\begin_inset space ~
\end_inset


\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand citep
key "Fri19"
literal "false"

\end_inset

:
\begin_inset Formula 
