\begin_inset Formula $\sum_{\kappa\in\mathcal{T}}\mathcal{B}_{\kappa}$
\end_inset

.
 The quantity 
\begin_inset Formula $S\left(y_{\kappa}(t_{i})\right)^{T}\mathsf{v}\left(y_{\kappa}(t_{i})\right)$
