\begin_inset Formula $\revisionmaththree{\tau}>0$
\end_inset

, we have 
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\sum_{\kappa\in\mathcal{T}}\mathcal{B}_{\kappa}\geq0.\label{eq:entropy-stability-proof-B-inequality}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

Combining Equations
